<h2>Installation</h2>
Our experienced design team will work directly with you or, if you prefer, your contractor or architect to create the perfect covered walkway for your application. After a design is specified, Solar Innovations<sup>¬Æ</sup> can provide a turn-key project. Everything from the fabrication to assembly to installation can be provided through Solar Innovations<sup>¬Æ</sup>. Based on the scope of your project, ¬†there are also ‚Äúdo-it-yourself ¬†installation kits‚Äù¬†available for those customers who would like to purchase the structure, but complete their own canopy installation. Solar Innovations<sup>¬Æ</sup> also offers repair to existing walkways when a complete new assembly is not necessary. No matter how simple or complex your walkway desires may be, Solar Innovations<sup>¬Æ</sup> will help you to create the perfect walkway for your application.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="37324" img_size="full"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_tta_tabs style="flat" shape="square" active_section="1"][vc_tta_section i_icon_fontawesome="fa fa-info-circle" add_icon="true" title="Product Overview" tab_id="1503414294912-bbc9bfab-822d"][vc_column_text]<a href="https://solarinnovations.com/wp-content/uploads/SI5000-Glazed-Structures-Cut-Sheet.pdf"><img class="alignright wp-image-25556 size-full" src="https://solarinnovations.com/wp-content/uploads/coverpage1.png" alt="" width="400" height="248" /></a>Solar Innovations<sup>¬Æ</sup> has been creating high quality durable Glazed Structures since 1998 for both commercial and residential applications, creating a line of functional accessories and decorative elements. In order to provide the highest quality products and offer a superior installation process, the Solar team pre-cuts and pre-drills each of the structural components before it is shipped. Unlike most greenhouse &amp; conservatory manufacturers, Solar Innovations<sup>¬Æ</sup> provides all the necessary fasteners, silicone, and flashings for your project. These services help customers reduce installation time and cost, providing a high quality final product.

